WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:05.104
<i>It all started when a time travel</i>
<i>experiment I was conducting... </i>

00:05.171 --> 00:08.106
<i>went... a little caca. </i>

00:09.542 --> 00:11.669
<i>In the blink of a cosmic clock,
I went from quantum physicist... </i>

00:11.745 --> 00:15.112
<i>... to air force test pilot,</i>

00:15.181 --> 00:18.582
<i>which could have been fun</i>
<i>if I knew how to fly. </i>

00:18.651 --> 00:21.916
<i>Fortunately, I had help,</i>
<i>an observer from the project named Al. </i>

00:21.988 --> 00:26.857
<i>Unfortunately, Al's a hologram,</i>
<i>so all he can lend is moral support. </i>

00:26.926 --> 00:29.918
<i>Anyway, here I am,</i>
<i>bouncing around in time,</i>

00:29.996 --> 00:32.089
<i>putting things right</i>
<i>that once went wrong</i>

00:32.165 --> 00:36.033
<i>a sort of time-traveling Lone Ranger</i>
<i>with Al as my Tonto,</i>

00:37.404 --> 00:39.565
<i>and I don't even need a mask. </i>

00:39.639 --> 00:41.573
Oh, boy.

